+# Requirements Tracker
+
+A zero-dependency Node.js requirements tracker that stores requirements in `requirements.json`.
+
+## Usage
+
+List requirements:
+
+```sh
+npm run demo
+node bin/reqs.js list
+```
+
+Add a requirement:
+
+```sh
+node bin/reqs.js add "Review acceptance criteria"
+```
+
+Toggle completion:
+
+```sh
+node bin/reqs.js toggle REQ-001
+```
+
+Run tests:
+
+```sh
+npm test
+```
